1
00:00:34,534 --> 00:00:35,874
Nueng,

2
00:00:35,874 --> 00:00:39,637
what are you doing here? It's almost time.

3
00:00:39,637 --> 00:00:43,234
Didn't Dad say he would be here soon?

4
00:00:43,234 --> 00:00:46,077
Your dad is meeting with some landowners from Macau.

5
00:00:46,077 --> 00:00:48,820
He said he would come as soon as possible after the meeting ended.

6
00:00:50,737 --> 00:00:53,254
Why don't you go and play the piano for me?

7
00:00:53,254 --> 00:00:55,484
It's been a long time since I heard you play the piano.

8
00:00:55,484 --> 00:00:59,564
I also want Dad to listen to the song that I've practiced.

9
00:00:59,564 --> 00:01:02,444
Do you not want me to listen to it then?

10
00:01:02,444 --> 00:01:04,674
I'm feeling hurt.

11
00:01:04,674 --> 00:01:06,384
Mom, please don't feel hurt.

12
00:01:06,384 --> 00:01:09,344
If Dad doesn't arrive in time, I'll play it for you.

13
00:01:09,344 --> 00:01:10,824
I'm already used to it.

14
00:01:10,824 --> 00:01:15,204
I understand that his work is more important than me.

15
00:01:15,204 --> 00:01:18,524
I'm glad that you understand him,

16
00:01:18,524 --> 00:01:21,084
so your dad doesn't have to worry about it.

17
00:01:21,674 --> 00:01:28,234
You know that he is working hard for you, don't you?

18
00:01:30,984 --> 00:01:35,614
How about this? When he gets here, I'll playfully tease him.

19
00:01:35,614 --> 00:01:37,794
How should I punish him? Help me think.

20
00:01:37,794 --> 00:01:39,734
What punishment?

21
00:01:39,734 --> 00:01:46,244
Why don't we ask him to tell you a bedtime story, just like he did when you were little?

22
00:01:46,244 --> 00:01:49,754
Mom, I'm not a child anymore. I'm turning eighteen today.

23
00:01:49,754 --> 00:01:50,884
Eighteen?

24
00:01:50,884 --> 00:01:53,754
Wow, my son is all grown up now.

25
00:01:53,754 --> 00:01:56,324
Can I still give you a kiss?

26
00:01:57,474 --> 00:01:59,504
Hum.

27
00:01:59,504 --> 00:02:01,468
What do you mean "hum"?

28
00:02:02,304 --> 00:02:04,214
Yes.

29
00:02:04,214 --> 00:02:06,254
How many kisses?

30
00:02:06,254 --> 00:02:08,340
Will you do it or not?

31
00:02:09,234 --> 00:02:12,024
Give me your other cheek.

32
00:02:13,724 --> 00:02:18,224
My son is grown up now.

33
00:02:52,614 --> 00:02:57,164
♪ Happy birthday to you ♪

34
00:02:57,164 --> 00:03:01,834
♪ Happy birthday to you ♪

35
00:03:01,834 --> 00:03:07,384
♪ Happy birthday, happy birthday ♪

36
00:03:07,384 --> 00:03:13,234
♪ Happy birthday to you ♪

37
00:03:14,474 --> 00:03:16,807
You said you had an important meeting.

38
00:03:16,807 --> 00:03:20,687
There's nothing more important than your eighteenth birthday.

39
00:03:21,900 --> 00:03:22,974
Blow the candles and

40
00:03:22,974 --> 00:03:24,254
don't forget to make a wish.

41
00:03:24,254 --> 00:03:28,814
I hope you stay healthy and safe,

42
00:03:28,814 --> 00:03:32,790
spend a lot of time with me, and will be with me for a long time.

43
00:03:33,644 --> 00:03:36,614
Why are your wishes about me? Why don't you make a wish for yourself?

44
00:03:36,614 --> 00:03:40,237
I have everything I want. What else could I need?

45
00:03:41,154 --> 00:03:42,794
Here.

46
00:03:43,864 --> 00:03:45,814
Okay.

47
00:03:47,384 --> 00:03:50,744
You are an adult now. You are eighteen.

48
00:03:50,744 --> 00:03:55,534
Are you interested in helping me manage the business?

49
00:03:55,534 --> 00:03:57,934
You could assist with running small errands in our hotel.

50
00:03:57,934 --> 00:04:00,234
Consider it an internship.

51
00:04:00,234 --> 00:04:05,034
Your ability to speak foreign languages, including English and Mandarin,

52
00:04:05,034 --> 00:04:07,774
means you won't have any problems communicating with the guests.

53
00:04:09,071 --> 00:04:12,604
I'm still in my last year of high school. Don't you think it's too early?

54
00:04:12,604 --> 00:04:14,224
It's not too soon at all.

55
00:04:14,224 --> 00:04:16,724
These days, you need to start working when you are young.

56
00:04:16,724 --> 00:04:18,702
Everything that I am building,

57
00:04:18,702 --> 00:04:23,294
I plan to hand it over to you one day.

58
00:04:23,294 --> 00:04:26,004
You are my only child,

59
00:04:26,004 --> 00:04:28,644
my hope.

60
00:04:34,544 --> 00:04:36,654
Don't you have something to give to him?

61
00:04:39,774 --> 00:04:42,774
I have a special gift for you.

62
00:04:42,774 --> 00:04:44,720
Open it.

63
00:04:54,354 --> 00:04:57,344
Do you know what the words mean?

64
00:05:00,447 --> 00:05:02,444
Wei Yi.

65
00:05:02,444 --> 00:05:04,024
It means only one.

66
00:05:04,024 --> 00:05:08,654
I wanted to give you this necklace.

67
00:05:08,654 --> 00:05:14,942
To tell you, Nuengdiao, that you are the only one

68
00:05:14,942 --> 00:05:18,944
who will protect our Kiattrakulmethee family after me.

69
00:05:18,944 --> 00:05:21,184
You are the only one that I trust.

70
00:05:21,184 --> 00:05:27,654
I hope you will grow up to be talented, decisive, and strong,

71
00:05:27,654 --> 00:05:31,944
and eventually, you will be the one to take over the businesses from me.

72
00:05:33,074 --> 00:05:36,734
Do you think you can do that for me?

73
00:05:44,284 --> 00:05:46,514
I'll do my best.

74
00:06:04,404 --> 00:06:08,034
I'd better go get the car so you don't have to walk in the rain.

75
00:06:08,034 --> 00:06:12,164
We can walk to the car with umbrellas, so we don't waste time waiting for you.

76
00:06:12,164 --> 00:06:14,464
I don't think it's a good idea. You will get wet.

77
00:06:14,464 --> 00:06:17,354
Young Master may get sick.

78
00:06:19,614 --> 00:06:21,434
- Go.
- Okay.

79
00:06:26,114 --> 00:06:27,634
Dad.

80
00:06:27,634 --> 00:06:30,484
My school is organizing an event for Father's Day,

81
00:06:30,484 --> 00:06:33,294
and they want you to attend and receive the Outstanding Father award.

82
00:06:33,294 --> 00:06:35,134
Can you go?

83
00:06:35,734 --> 00:06:37,654
"Outstanding father"?

84
00:06:37,654 --> 00:06:40,354
I don't think I'm the right person for the award.

85
00:06:40,354 --> 00:06:42,624
I want you to go.

86
00:06:45,424 --> 00:06:48,424
If that's what you want, then I will go.

87
00:06:48,424 --> 00:06:53,034
If your friends tease you about it, I can't help you with that.

88
00:06:53,034 --> 00:06:56,417
They can tease me all they want. I still want you to go.

89
00:06:57,174 --> 00:06:59,984
You two are just talking to each other. I guess you forgot about me.

90
00:06:59,984 --> 00:07:04,014
- No, we didn't.
- Mom, don't worry.

91
00:07:04,014 --> 00:07:05,914
We can all go together.

92
00:07:05,914 --> 00:07:08,714
I'm not raising him alone.

93
00:07:08,714 --> 00:07:12,994
How can our family forget a kind mother like you?

94
00:07:12,994 --> 00:07:14,584
Right?

95
00:07:15,930 --> 00:07:17,310
He's right.

96
00:07:17,310 --> 00:07:19,190
Don't worry. Wait until Mother's Day.

97
00:07:19,194 --> 00:07:22,044
- What?
- Wait until Mother's Day.

98
00:07:28,744 --> 00:07:31,174
- Piphop!
- Dad!

99
00:07:33,534 --> 00:07:36,659
Dad! Dad!

100
00:07:36,659 --> 00:07:38,094
Dad, hang on dad!

101
00:07:38,094 --> 00:07:39,584
Dad, stay with me.

102
00:07:39,584 --> 00:07:42,024
Dad, put pressure on the wound.

103
00:07:53,120 --> 00:07:54,740
Stop!

104
00:07:55,454 --> 00:07:56,784
Piphop!

105
00:07:56,784 --> 00:07:59,594
Uncle Non, call an ambulance!

106
00:07:59,594 --> 00:08:01,337
Hurry, call an ambulance!

107
00:08:01,337 --> 00:08:03,964
Uncle Non, please hurry!

108
00:08:03,964 --> 00:08:11,254
I don't think I can make it to your school event.

109
00:08:11,254 --> 00:08:12,704
Dad, don't say that.

110
00:08:12,704 --> 00:08:15,774
Dad please hang on. The ambulance will be here soon.

111
00:08:15,774 --> 00:08:17,224
Stay with me.

112
00:08:17,224 --> 00:08:21,034
I will always be with you.

113
00:08:21,914 --> 00:08:24,204
No. Please don't say that.

114
00:08:24,204 --> 00:08:26,280
I'm not ready yet. You can't leave me.

115
00:08:26,280 --> 00:08:29,180
- There are still many things that I need to learn from you.
- Pop.

116
00:08:31,350 --> 00:08:35,034
Nueng, I love you.

117
00:08:35,034 --> 00:08:43,054
Please take care of everything for me.

118
00:08:43,054 --> 00:08:45,174
No. Dad, don't say that.

119
00:08:45,174 --> 00:08:47,324
Stay with me, Dad.

120
00:08:47,324 --> 00:08:51,044
Dad, hang on. The ambulance will be here soon.

121
00:08:51,044 --> 00:08:53,684
Dad. No, I'm not ready!

122
00:08:53,684 --> 00:08:56,134
Dad!

