143
00:10:40,764 --> 00:10:43,044
Don't worry about me.

144
00:10:43,044 --> 00:10:46,124
Everything will go well.

145
00:10:47,174 --> 00:10:49,697
Even though your dad is not here,

146
00:10:49,697 --> 00:10:54,527
you and I will take care of everything for him.

147
00:10:56,474 --> 00:10:58,124
Nueng,

148
00:10:59,276 --> 00:11:01,373
remember what I said.

149
00:11:02,774 --> 00:11:05,384
One day, when you are ready,

150
00:11:06,384 --> 00:11:09,890
you will step up to take care of everything in the company.

151
00:11:10,644 --> 00:11:14,794
You will take care of everything in our family, just like your dad did.

152
00:11:16,604 --> 00:11:21,184
You are the only hope of the Kiattrakulmethee.

153
00:11:26,294 --> 00:11:28,004
Yes, Mom.

154
00:12:01,444 --> 00:12:06,124
Khun Tanya, do you have any updates on Piphop's murder case?
(T/N: Khun is a way to politely address someone)

155
00:12:06,124 --> 00:12:08,104
Right now, I can't provide you with any information about the case,

156
00:12:08,104 --> 00:12:11,684
as the police are concerned that it might impact the ongoing investigation.

157
00:12:11,684 --> 00:12:14,034
There has been some progress in the investigation.

158
00:12:14,034 --> 00:12:19,164
Is it true that his attack was motivated by a conflict in his underground business?

159
00:12:19,164 --> 00:12:20,805
Is that so?

160
00:12:20,805 --> 00:12:26,480
Can you please tell me what underground business you are talking about?

161
00:12:26,480 --> 00:12:31,234
What kind of business conflict was it? I'm curious to hear it, too.

162
00:12:31,234 --> 00:12:34,828
It may be useful for the investigation.

163
00:12:34,828 --> 00:12:39,005
If you have the information, please submit it to the police.

164
00:12:39,005 --> 00:12:40,716
We need all the help we can get.

165
00:12:40,716 --> 00:12:43,243
What about the future of the business?

166
00:12:43,243 --> 00:12:45,739
Who will be the next CEO after Khun Piphop?

167
00:12:45,739 --> 00:12:47,716
Please provide us with that information.

168
00:12:57,144 --> 00:13:02,036
I, Tanya Kiattrakulmethee,

169
00:13:02,036 --> 00:13:07,560
will take over the CEO position for every company...

170
00:13:08,220 --> 00:13:10,790
in the conglomerate after Khun Piphop.

171
00:14:18,959 --> 00:14:21,965
Excuse me, Sir. May I ask some questions, please?

172
00:14:21,965 --> 00:14:23,679
May I ask some questions, please?

173
00:14:23,679 --> 00:14:24,722
Okay.

174
00:14:24,722 --> 00:14:26,593
Due to the current situation,

175
00:14:26,593 --> 00:14:28,817
what is your opinion on the concern of the shareholders

176
00:14:28,817 --> 00:14:33,399
that the revenue and profit may decline after the president is gone?

177
00:14:36,376 --> 00:14:39,039
I'm not worried about this issue.

178
00:14:39,039 --> 00:14:41,680
Our businesses aren't dictated by one person.

179
00:14:41,680 --> 00:14:46,114
And we are using the same operational teams and employees as before.

180
00:14:46,114 --> 00:14:49,747
So yes, I'm absolutely sure that we're going to be fine.

181
00:14:49,747 --> 00:14:52,936
Thank you.

182
00:14:55,535 --> 00:14:57,333
Pull it in.

183
00:14:58,091 --> 00:15:00,483
Pull it. Pull it up.

184
00:15:00,483 --> 00:15:02,430
Okay.

185
00:15:06,006 --> 00:15:08,473
Hey, Palm, why don't you buy your own boat?

186
00:15:08,473 --> 00:15:12,922
I'm sure you will be a good captain.

187
00:15:12,922 --> 00:15:16,123
Buy a boat? I don't have any money.

188
00:15:16,123 --> 00:15:18,214
Purchasing a motorcycle is already a significant expense for me.

189
00:15:18,214 --> 00:15:22,181
If I had money, do you think I would use it to buy a boat?

190
00:15:22,181 --> 00:15:24,827
There is no hope here.

191
00:15:24,827 --> 00:15:27,593
