196
00:15:39,953 --> 00:15:43,693
I think you will definitely go to college, am I right?

197
00:15:44,818 --> 00:15:46,169
I don't know.

198
00:15:46,169 --> 00:15:47,942
What else can I do

199
00:15:47,942 --> 00:15:52,673
besides catching fish, playing sports, and manual labor?

200
00:15:52,673 --> 00:15:55,680
You need to have a dream.

